    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use resonant crystals to stimulate wound healing. When you use at least two semiprecious stones with a total value of at least 50 gp, you can use Occultism instead of Medicine to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1kGNdIIhuglAjIp9], including higher Occultism proficiency letting you attempt more difficult checks. It doesn’t replace Medicine for uses of the skill other than Treat Wounds or for feat prerequisites.</p><p>The bonuses from @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.6O8MoMheHs5hNHX1] also apply when you use Crystal Medicine.</p><p></p>",
